<subSubSection pageId="98" pageNumber="99" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="98" pageNumber="99">
≡ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Chenopodiacea" genus="Chenopodium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Chenopodium scoparium" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="98" pageNumber="99" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="scoparium">Chenopodium scoparium</taxonomicName>
L., Sp. Pl.: 221 (1753). 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="98" pageNumber="99">Lectotype</emphasis>
(designated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Jafri, SMH" journalOrPublisher="6. Akademiya Nauk, Moscow-Leningrad" pageId="127" pageNumber="128" refId="B50" refString="Jafri, SMH, Rateeb, FB, 1978. Chenopodiaceae. In: Jafri SMH, El-Gadi A (Eds) Flora of Libya, Vol. 58. Al Faateh University, Tripoli." title="Chenopodiaceae. In: Jafri SMH, El-Gadi A (Eds) Flora of Libya, Vol. 58. Al Faateh University, Tripoli." year="1978">Jafri and Rateeb 1978</bibRefCitation>
): Herb. Linn. 313.20 (LINN! image available at http://linnean-online.org/3145/).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="98" pageNumber="99">
≡ 
<taxonomicName authority="" authorityName="" class="Rosopsida" family="Chenopodiacea" genus="Kochia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Kochia scoparia" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="98" pageNumber="99" phylum="Magnoliophyta" rank="species" species="scoparia">Kochia scoparia</taxonomicName>
(L.) Schrad., Neues J. Bot. 3(3-4): 85 (1809). Comprehensive list of synonymic names of 
<taxonomicName family="Chenopodiacea" genus="B." higherTaxonomySource="treatment-meta" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. scoparia" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="98" pageNumber="99" rank="species" species="scoparia">B. scoparia</taxonomicName>
is presented in 
<bibRefCitation author="Sukhorukov, AP" journalOrPublisher="Willdenowia" pageId="130" pageNumber="131" refId="B107" refString="Sukhorukov, AP, 2014. The carpology of the Chenopodiaceae with reference to the phylogeny, systematics and diagnostics of its representatives. Grif &amp; Co., Tula. [in Russian with English summary]" title="The carpology of the Chenopodiaceae with reference to the phylogeny, systematics and diagnostics of its representatives. Grif &amp; Co., Tula. [in Russian with English summary]" year="2014">Sukhorukov (2014)</bibRefCitation>
